      "content": "I would like the story of Reliance to be told in that book which has no final chapter and one which is continually updated with records of bolder initiatives and more glittering successes, and where successive generations create even greater societal value and contribute to India's growth.\n\n**Shri Mukesh D. Ambani**Chairman & Managing Director\n\n![](_page_1_Picture_7.jpeg)\n\nBY MARKET CAPITALISATION\n\n₹17,81,841 crore\n\n**BY REVENUE** \n\n₹7,92,756 crore\n\n**BY NET PROFIT** \n\n₹67,845 crore\n\nOne of the highest contributors to India's economic growth\n\nReliance Industries Limited (RIL)\n\nand the largest private sector\n\ncreator and the highest valued company.\n\nWith a strongly integrated energy business and the most expansive digital and retail footprint in the country, RIL is India's largest corporate value\n\nis a Fortune 500 company\n\ncorporation in India.\n\n**EXPORTS** \n\n₹2,54,970 crore\n\n**COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT** \n\n₹1,186 crore\n\n**EMPLOYMENT CREATION** \n\n2,32,822\n\n,",
